additional_data.description: A water spirit, one of the four main elementals. Most of her body is made up of liquid. Once this liquid was pure water, but due to an unparalled love of liquor, she is now mostly made of alcohol. She was originally a spirit of good lineage, but an unrequited love drove her to drink and made her what she is today.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "The Spirits' Doll Festival" Event: Clear Chapter 1
◦ "The Spirits' Doll Festival" Event: Exchange for 200 Hishi Mochi.
◦ "The Spirits' Doll Festival" Event: Get a Second Half Ranking of 6001-10000.
◦ "The Spirits' Doll Festival" Event: Get a Total Ranking of 7501-10000.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ Slightly increases the drop rate of Hishi Mochi during the "The Spirits' Doll Festival" event.

main: "We might as well drink together, don't you think?"
summon: "I can tell you anything you want to know about booze."
limit_break: "Woo, I'm starting to feel it now."
